{"tid":1142833,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"話說我公司搞左個華麗睡衣派對","createTime":"2019-05-07T10:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T03:11:52.000Z","uid":21742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7d38b1243364536f50059aa387592cef2b5856","tid":1142833,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kx3MuiZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkx3MuiZ.png&h=511c81da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講啲背景先<br />\n<br />\n我公司係做飲食，唔多唔少都有10幾間分店<br />\n<br />\n而我公司上至70歲既洗碗阿姐下至18歲既靚仔都有<br />\n<br />\n除左後生妹之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身週年聚餐呢啲我都ok<br />\n<br />\n但問題係成<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11點</span></span>先開始<br />\n<br />\n而當日同翌日都係要返12至10<br />\n<br />\n聽之前去過既同事講，多數搞到凌晨3,4點先走<br />\n<br />\n重要自己比錢搭的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底啲所謂高層要幾痴線先諗到搞個咁既聚會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da1e61bc3817e14c455c964438f77fcc7555427","tid":1142833,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472c62687d6bf8ac0b5d374a8d57e4f482edc6a1","tid":1142833,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f5efc66ab5656167ecc3c0dccdc25784ea1cab","tid":1142833,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bb7ca9e591f3a97bdd5ed1357860211724c3bb","tid":1142833,"uid":130421,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20